Uses of Package
nl.naturalis.geneious

  • Packages that use nl.naturalis.geneious 
    Package Description
    nl.naturalis.geneious
    Foundational classes and interfaces for the Naturalis Geneious plugin.
    nl.naturalis.geneious.bold
    Classes and interfaces dedicated to the BOLD Import operation.
    nl.naturalis.geneious.crs
    Classes and interfaces dedicated to the CRS Import operation.
    nl.naturalis.geneious.csv
    Classes and interfaces shared by all operations that import CSV or CSV-like files (including spreadsheets).
    nl.naturalis.geneious.name
    Classes and interfaces shared by the AB1/Fasta Import operation and the Split Name operation.
    nl.naturalis.geneious.seq
    Classes and interfaces dedicated to the AB1/Fasta Import operation.
    nl.naturalis.geneious.smpl
    Classes and interfaces dedicated to the Sample Sheet Import operation.
    nl.naturalis.geneious.split
    Classes and interfaces dedicated to the Split Name operation.
    nl.naturalis.geneious.util
    Utility classes.
  • Classes in nl.naturalis.geneious used by nl.naturalis.geneious 
    Class Description
    DocumentType
    Symbolic constants for all document types that the Naturalis plugin deals with.
    GlobalOptions
    An object underpinning the Tools -> Preferences panel.
    NonFatalException
    A NonFatalException is an exception that prevents an operation from proceeding any further, but does not warrant presenting the user with a "scary" stack trace.
    OperationConfig
    Base class for objects capturing the user input and other configuration data for one of the plugin's operations.
    PluginInfo
    Contains and provides version-related information showin in the Tools -> Preferences panel.
    Precondition
    Symbolic constants for preconditions that must be met before an operation is allowed to commence.
    Setting
    Symbolic constants for the available configuration settings for the Naturalis plugin.
    Settings
    Provides access to the settings in the Tools -> Preferences tab.
    StoredDocument
    A wrapper around the AnnotatedPluginDocument class with all of its Naturalis-specific annotations pre-fetched into a NaturalisNote instance.
